    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1176422441">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1176422441" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1176422441" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1176422441">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/121284238/">思惜宇</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">个人认为，还是台版翻译为“记忆所系之处”更加恰当。由于对“场”一字的普遍认识，“记忆之场”总容易让人以为是记忆建构的场所，那么这就大大限制了对诺拉定义的理解了。而由“所系之处”代替“场”，倒是能相当程度上规避这一误读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

